trans-unit.source: Associates a well-known object type that is passed to the Web Services Description Language (WSDL) generator with a remote endpoint that can process messages that are sent to a method on the type.
trans-unit.target: Associerar ett välkänt objekt-typ som har skickats till generatorn Web Services WSDL (Description Language) med en fjärrslutpunkten som kan bearbeta meddelanden som skickas till en metod i typen.

trans-unit.source: The ServiceType class is used to hold information that is specified on the command line to the [Soapsuds Tool (Soapsuds.exe)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/40f6f8c8-b80c-4e9f-a920-31bcd0cf45c5) through the `-types` argument.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ServiceType används för att lagra information som har angetts på kommandoraden för att den [Soapsuds verktyget (Soapsuds.exe)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/40f6f8c8-b80c-4e9f-a920-31bcd0cf45c5) via den `-types` argumentet.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.ServiceType"></xref> class with the object <xref:System.Type> that is passed to the Web Services Description Language (WSDL) generator.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.ServiceType"> </xref> klass med objektet <xref:System.Type>som har skickats till generatorn för Web Services WSDL (Description Language).</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The object <xref:System.Type> that is passed to the WSDL generator.

Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.ServiceType"></xref> class with the URL and <xref:System.Type> of an object that is passed to the Web Services Description Language (WSDL) generator.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.ServiceType"> </xref> klass med URL: en och <xref:System.Type>för ett objekt som har skickats till generatorn för Web Services WSDL (Description Language).</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The object <xref:System.Type> that is passed to the WSDL generator.
The well-known endpoint that can process messages that are sent to a method on the object type that is specified in the `type` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Välkända slutpunkten som kan bearbeta meddelanden som skickas till en metod på den objekttyp som anges i den `type` parameter.

trans-unit.source: Gets the object <xref:System.Type> that is passed to the Web Services Description Language (WSDL) generator.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar objektet <xref:System.Type>som har skickats till generatorn för Web Services WSDL (Description Language).</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The object <xref:System.Type> that the current <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.ServiceType"></xref> was created for.
Gets the URL of an object <xref:System.Type> that is passed to the Web Services Description Language (WSDL) generator.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar URL för ett objekt <xref:System.Type>som har skickats till generatorn för Web Services WSDL (Description Language).</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The URL of an object <xref:System.Type> that the current <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.ServiceType"></xref> was created for.
trans-unit.target: URL-Adressen för ett objekt <xref:System.Type>som aktuellt <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.ServiceType"> </xref> skapades för</xref:System.Type>
